{"type":"answer","id":55638,"parentType":"question","parentId":12794,"uid":7290,"contents":"为了解决歪脖子树成活率不高的老大难问题，习近平总书记高瞻远瞩，青年时期，在梁家河山路上，用巧劲儿单肩扛麦的时候就已经把脖子压歪了，所以在他眼中哪棵都是歪脖子树，从根本上解决了歪脖子树的种植问题。<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EWxyP08XgAIIXZR?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EWxyP08XgAIIXZR?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EWxyP08XgAIIXZR?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-10-10","agreeCount":2,"discussionCount":0}